OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779117068
OL,3,CSchools shut over fears play sand
OL,4,Ccould contain asbestos
OL,6,FSchools have been closed on North
OL,7,FTyneside over fears play sand used in
OL,8,Fclassrooms could be contaminated with
OL,9,Fasbestos.
OL,11,FNorth Tyneside Council has confirmed
OL,12,Ftwo schools are closed, while a third
OL,13,Fhas had partial classroom closures but
OL,14,Fhas re-opened.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
