OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779117068
OL,3,CSchools shut over fears play sand
OL,4,Ccould contain asbestos
OL,6,FCouncil representatives said officials
OL,7,Fhad acted "immediately" to support
OL,8,Fschools in restricting access to areas
OL,9,Fwhere play sand was used.
OL,11,FThe Health and Safety Executive and UK
OL,12,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA) have
OL,13,Fboth been involved in supporting the
OL,14,Fcouncil's response.
OL,16,FIt is understood that play sand has
OL,17,Fbeen purchased at reputable high
OL,18,Fstreet retailers. The council believes
OL,19,Fthis to be a wider national issue,
OL,20,Frather than one confined to the
OL,21,Fborough.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
