FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779117068
OL,3,CSchools shut over fears play sand
OL,4,Ccould contain asbestos
OL,6,FIn a post on Wednesday, Beacon Hill
OL,7,FSchool said: "Beacon Hill School and
OL,8,Fsixth form will be closed for the next
OL,9,Ftwo days while we await the results of
OL,10,Fsamples taken from sand on the school
OL,11,Fsite following concerns about a
OL,12,Fpotential but low asbestos risk."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
