FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779117068
OL,3,CSchools shut over fears play sand
OL,4,Ccould contain asbestos
OL,6,FRebecca Wall, director of children's
OL,7,Fservices at North Tyneside Council,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Keeping pupils and staff safe
OL,9,Fis our top priority, and we take this
OL,10,Fresponsibility extremely seriously.
OL,12,F"Earlier this week, we became aware of
OL,13,Fwider concerns linked to a national
OL,14,Fproduct recall involving play sand and
OL,15,Fthe potential presence of asbestos. We
OL,16,Facted immediately to support schools
OL,17,Fin temporarily restricting access to
OL,18,Fareas where play sand is used,
OL,19,Fproviding reassurance while further
OL,20,Fchecks are carried out.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779117068
OL,3,CSchools shut over fears play sand
OL,4,Ccould contain asbestos
OL,6,F"Temporarily closing schools is never
OL,7,Fa decision we take lightly. However,
OL,8,Fdue to the significant quantities of
OL,9,Fplay sand on site at Beacon Hill and
OL,10,FSilverdale Schools and following
OL,11,Fguidance from the Health and Safety
OL,12,FExecutive, we have advised that both
OL,13,Fschools temporarily close as a
OL,14,Fprecautionary measure.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779117068
OL,3,CSchools shut over fears play sand
OL,4,Ccould contain asbestos
OL,6,F"I want to reassure parents, pupils,
OL,7,Fand staff that advice from the UK
OL,8,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,9,Findicates the overall risk to health
OL,10,Fis low. However, we are committed to
OL,11,Ffollowing national guidance and taking
OL,12,Fa cautious, safety-first approach.
OL,14,F"We continue to work closely with the
OL,15,FUK Health Security Agency and other
OL,16,Fnational partners to ensure a
OL,17,Fcoordinated and precautionary
OL,18,Fresponse."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
