FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779117068
OL,3,CSchools shut over fears play sand
OL,4,Ccould contain asbestos
OL,6,FThe Office for Product Safety and
OL,7,FStandards (OPSS) said on Wednesday 13
OL,8,FMay they are aware of products in the
OL,9,FUK containing sand contaminated with
OL,10,Fasbestos.
OL,12,FThey said schools and early years
OL,13,Fproviders should follow their
OL,14,Fguidelines for identifying and
OL,15,Fdisposing affected products.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
